  FREE for: personal research/study/hobby use, and for academic research,
  classroom instruction, and software verification -- but ONLY on systems
  deployed specifically for those purposes (test/research systems), never on
  the institution's operational/live systems, and never to process live data.

  REQUIRES A PAID COMMERCIAL LICENSE for: any operational use, including
  security monitoring, digital forensics, and incident response performed to
  conduct, protect, defend, or investigate an organization's own systems,
  networks, data, or operations -- regardless of the organization's nonprofit,
  educational, governmental, or charitable status. See COMMERCIAL.md.

